OL,3,CA5 upgrade plan breaches climate law,
OL,4,Cjudge rules
OL,6,FA judge has ruled that the #1.2billion
OL,7,Ffirst phase of the A5 project cannot
OL,8,Fgo ahead in its current form because
OL,9,Fthe plans do not comply with climate
OL,10,Fchange laws in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FA summary of the 100 page document was
OL,13,Fpresented by Judge McAlinden to a
OL,14,Fpacked Belfast courtroom that included
OL,15,FMinister for Infrastructure Liz
OL,16,FKimmins, campaigners, those against
OL,17,Fthe proposed scheme, and the press.
