OL,3,CA5 upgrade plan breaches climate law,
OL,4,Cjudge rules
OL,6,FLast year the Department for
OL,7,FInfrastructure (DFI) announced it was
OL,8,Fgoing to build the controversial dual
OL,9,Fcarriageway linking Derry with Tyrone.
OL,11,FThe Northern Ireland Executive gave
OL,12,Fthe green light for the long-awaited
OL,13,Fupgrade to the A5 in October.
OL,14,FPreparatory work had already started
OL,15,Fon the new route near Ballygawley,
OL,16,Fincluding the clearing of land.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
