OL,3,CA5 upgrade plan breaches climate law,
OL,4,Cjudge rules
OL,6,FHowever, a group known as the A5
OL,7,FAlternative Alliance brought a legal
OL,8,Fchallenge against the decision
OL,9,Fclaiming the plan breaches climate
OL,10,Fchange legislation set out in the
OL,11,FClimate Change (Northern Ireland) Act
OL,12,F2022 to achieve net-zero greenhouse
OL,13,Fgas emissions by 2050.
OL,15,FMr Justice McAlinden ruled there was
OL,16,Fan "inadequacy of information for the
OL,17,Fpurpose of lawful decision making"
OL,18,Fwhen it comes to the methodology of
OL,19,Festimating greenhouse gas emissions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
