OL,3,CA5 upgrade plan breaches climate law,
OL,4,Cjudge rules
OL,6,F"It would appear that overall,
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland may have difficulty
OL,8,Fstaying within the first carbon budget
OL,9,Fthat has now been set," he said.
OL,11,FThe judge also made reference to
OL,12,Fconcerns over human rights saying that
OL,13,Fthe DFI "patently failed to address
OL,14,Fthe human rights concerns" of some of
OL,15,Fthose affected who live along the
OL,16,Froute of the new proposed road.
