OL,3,CA5 upgrade plan breaches climate law,
OL,4,Cjudge rules
OL,6,FIt is estimated the project will
OL,7,Ftemporarily affect direct access to
OL,8,Fmore than 130 residential properties
OL,9,Fand will necessitate the demolition of
OL,10,Fthree resident dwellings.
OL,12,FSince 2006, more than 50 people have
OL,13,Fbeen killed on the road and
OL,14,Fcampaigners claim the upgrade would
OL,15,Fsave lives.
OL,17,FJustice McAlinden said he was aware
OL,18,Fthe decision will bring "fresh anguish
OL,19,Fto the doors of those who have been
OL,20,Finjured and maimed and those who have
OL,21,Flost loved ones".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
