OL,3,CA5 upgrade plan breaches climate law,
OL,4,Cjudge rules
OL,6,F"However the decision to proceed with
OL,7,Fthe scheme must be in accordance with
OL,8,Fthe law and and the principle of the
OL,9,Frule of law cannot be subverted even
OL,10,Fif the motivation for doing so is to
OL,11,Fachieve what is deemed to constitute a
OL,12,Fclear societal benefit."
OL,14,FThe judge added that the
OL,15,F"shortcomings" and "short cuts"
OL,16,Fhighlighted in this decision are
OL,17,Fcapable of being remedied and should
OL,18,Fbe done sooner rather than later so a
OL,19,Fnew and safer A5 dual carriageway
OL,20,Fcould be built.
